<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en"
      xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
      xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
      xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"
      lang="en"
      metal:use-macro="context/main_template/macros/master"
      i18n:domain="plone">

<head>
  <metal:css fill-slot="css_slot">
    <style type="text/css">

    </style>
  </metal:css>
</head>
<body>
<metal:main fill-slot="main">
<h1 class="documentFirstHeading">Opengever Icons test page</h1>

<div class="documentDescription">
Hier werden alle Icons angezeigt. Die Seite soll helfen, zu überprüfen ob alle Icons korrekt sind.
</div>
<div id="dashboard-portlets1">
    <h2>Content Types</h2>
    <dl tal:define="types view/content_types">
        <dt tal:repeat="item types">
            <label tal:attributes="class string:contenttype-${item/extra/id};
                                   for string:form-field-${item/extra/id};">
                <img tal:attributes="src item/icon" alt="" />
                <span tal:replace="item/title">Type title</span>
            </label>
            <pre tal:content="string:contenttype-${item/extra/id}"/>
        </dt>    
    </dl>
</div>
<div id="dashboard-portlets2">
    <h2>Workflow States</h2>
</div>
<div id="dashboard-portlets3">
    <h2>Mimetype Icons</h2>
</div>
<div class="visualClear"><!-- IE Fix --></div>
</metal:main>

</body>
</html>
